'''George Orwell''' ({{bd|1903-ngièn|6-ngie̍t 25-ngit|1950-ngièn|1-ngie̍t 21-ngit}}), ngièn-lòi miàng-sṳ ham cho '''Eric Arthur Blair''', he [[Yîn-koet]] ke yit chak chok-kâ.

Kì chhut-miàng ke chok-phín yù ''[[Thung-vu̍t Nùng-chhòng]]'' (''Animal Farm'') lâu ''[[Yit kiú pat si]]'' (''Nineteen Eighty-Four'').

